data.description: This delightful property offers an exciting opportunity for those seeking a starter home with great potential or an investment venture in the heart of Ball Ground, GA, a town steeped in rich history and character. Nestled within a quaint neighborhood, this residence features three bedrooms and two bathrooms, presenting the canvas for your unique vision. With a bit of TLC, this home can be transformed into an ideal starter home or a profitable investment opportunity. The home has hardwood floors throughout and all appliances, including washer and dryer, convey with the sale of the home. The generous lot boasts mature trees and landscaping, providing a serene backdrop for potential outdoor enhancements. Home is sold as is.
